quran[20]{c,v,t}:
  55,26,Everyone upon it is perishing
  55,27,"But will remain the Presence of your Lord, Full of Majesty and Splendor"
  55,28,So which of your Lord's marvels will you deny
  55,29,Everyone in the heavens and the earth asks Him. Every day He is managing
  55,30,So which of your Lord's marvels will you deny
  55,31,"We will attend to you, O prominent two"
  55,32,So which of your Lord's marvels will you deny
  55,33,"O society of jinn and humans! If you can pass through the bounds of the heavens and the earth, go ahead and pass. But you will not pass except with authorization"
  55,34,So which of your Lord's marvels will you deny
  55,35,"You will be bombarded with flares of fire and brass, and you will not succeed"
  55,36,So which of your Lord's marvels will you deny
  55,37,"When the sky splits apart, and becomes rose, like paint"
  55,38,So which of your Lord's marvels will you deny
  55,39,"On that Day, no human and no jinn will be asked about his sins"
  55,40,So which of your Lord's marvels will you deny
  55,41,The guilty will be recognized by their marks; they will be taken by the forelocks and the feet
  55,42,So which of your Lord's marvels will you deny
  55,43,This is Hell that the guilty denied
  55,44,They circulate between it and between a seething bath
  55,45,So which of your Lord's marvels will you deny